            "body": "Yes, this feels fragile. Although I haven't really ran into the problem in my own version of this, core has to be more stable. \n\nYesterday I started experimenting with changing the message content to be empty using the corresponding id:\n\n```lua\nnvim_echo({ { ''} }, { id = 'nvim.diagnostic.ui2.<bufnr>.<linenr>', kind = 'empty' })\n```",
